column5: Anything to be had in the Grand by Dunnville right now?  Thanks,  LTF
Now that they changed the wind forecast, I think I might go out of Port Maitland for bass
Tues Wed looks good, high winds again Thursday at noon. Got to check everyday before heading out. Bass are biting at Gull Rock. Tube jigs.
I'm guessing if I launch at fishmasters, he will be able to point me in the right direction. Not really sure where gull rock is...
